ID.description: ID is the identifier of the object.

dataTypes.description: A list of all the data types which are associated to this data set.

description.description: Description of the custom data set.

importHash.description: The hash of the structure used to compare with new import version.

importLabel.description:
The user-defined import label that allows the system to group resources from the
same import operation.

name.description:
The internal reference name of the object. It is a sanitized version of Friendly
Name if empty.

propagate.description: Propagates the object to all child namespaces. This is always true.

updateTime.description: Last update date of the object.
